    {
      "id": "08b05a58-78f6-4529-9970-2dccff3cd473",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Thus, the paper starts with the introduction of a framework that intends to identify what are the unknown unknowns - reasons for why a student failed and that the model was blind to. The mdeol is verified using data from flipped and online courses. It also combines quantitative analysis with instructor interviews. ",
